{"tid":1109951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得其實杜生都幾慘","createTime":"2019-04-16T11:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T13:15:32.000Z","uid":2719,"like":30,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff324c052e91b14c9af6d64ef675081fc54dbdb","tid":1109951,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"全程都係女方主動<br />\n杜生一係推開 一係跳車<br />\n講緊係黃心穎 假假地都叫係香港小姐<br />\n咁大對波壓埋黎 再嘴 你話我咸濕都好<br />\n有幾多男人反抗到？<br />\n杜生明顯已經不知所措到隻手唔知放邊<br />\n揸嘅攬嘅就內心責備 推開又抵受唔住<br />\n<br />\n局外人或女人咪可以懶道徳咁批評囉<br />\n但如果主角換轉係你 肯定沉 甚至更甚<br />\n<br />\n根本成件事都係幸福的災難<br />\n無得避 都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n話推開乜柒嘅偽君子死全家"},{"pid":"303ef1ce2bc21131fe2eee319f00de8468bc574d","tid":1109951,"uid":20241,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"講真屌安仔既撚屌只不過因為自己冇機會食好野<br />\n係度葡萄人<br />\n心穎俾你屌你咪又狗衝<br />\n你老尾又話人地賓賓又盛<br />\n個心就恨都恨唔來"},{"pid":"c6bc6b270b50a720d06a084b79cecf7f5360c8a8","tid":1109951,"uid":14423,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"俾我已經可能揸咗波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102049c8fff87a738b45745804ac25985dc09b2f","tid":1109951,"uid":58140,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"以普通人咁諗好正常<br />\n但你藝人嚟 仲要有老婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43784bb9eb61c4aea769d9014bdc26317af3a02c","tid":1109951,"uid":96182,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"傻啦一黎就咁熟手你方係第一次咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩車到走唔甩就藉口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540f7ce6d8135605bf565a3ee256351157a6b9a7","tid":1109951,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6bc6b270b50a720d06a084b79cecf7f5360c8a8","tid":1109951,"uid":14423,